Name:           Arch-Demon
Short Name:     arch
Level Required: 29

Description:
  The most powerful of all summoned creatures, the Arch-Demon is
  extremely hard to control. It has all powers of the Demon Lord
  and can also summon Hellfire to blast all its foes.

Commands:
  - summon arch:    Summons it to you         (costs 400 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cter <monster>: Makes <monster> flee      (costs 50 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban arch:       Banishes it               (costs 50 sp)
